docs {
  ### Delete Invoice Payment (TESTING ONLY)
  Performs a soft delete on a specific invoice payment entry.
  
  **Path Parameters:**
  - `id`: The UUID of the payment entry.
  
  **Success Response (200 OK):**
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "code": 200,
    "message": "Successfully deleted",
    "data": null
  }
  ```
}
